  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting Comprehensive Language Initiatives &#x2013; Phase 3</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To advance the implementation of the recommendations developed during the United Nations Kosovo Trust-Building Forum, promote language rights and maintain the initiative&apos;s momentum, IOM will provide ongoing support to communities to come together and demonstrate their commitment to the process of trust-building. This project supports further development of Albanian/Serbian and Serbian/Albanian curriculum, further development of the online dictionary, and support to ensure the sustainability of these language education initiatives through embedding them in the University of Pristina.</narrative>
  </description>
